data.description: *** FHA Approved / ADU Potential *** OVER $20k in upgrades with a 6,098 Sq Ft lot located adjacent to the home. This charming starter home presents an ideal entry into homeownership, offering a solid foundation for those embarking on their real estate journey. While it exudes potential and character, a discerning eye will recognize the opportunity for personalization and improvement. The residence beckons with a cozy ambiance and promises a canvas for creative enhancement.  This home offers you newer tile and baseboards with newer paint and recessed lighting throughout. New anti-bacterial lighting, heater, and fan in bathroom. Ceiling fans in every room. Brand new induction range. LG convection oven stove. Newer LG energy efficient dishwasher. Three ceiling mini split air conditioning/ heating system. Water resistance front yard.   Complementary washer and dryer. Large and small shed. Both appropriate for working in or storage. This home is ready for the person to take it to the next level.
